description: Pharrell`s Dusknoir battled against Nikola`s Fletchinder where it proved its Ghost type moves were good at avoiding attacks but Nikola`s Fletchinder endured a direct hit from Thunder Punch. It was a quick battle and Nikola`s Fletchinder won the battle against Pharrell`s Dusknoir.
name: Yonoir (Pharrell)
